Hi there,

When testing React and Formsy in Node you need to load up JSDOM. At least currently. This is also required by other libraries so please do something like this in your test setup:

``` js
var jsdom = require("jsdom").jsdom;
global.document = jsdom();
global.window = document.defaultView;
global.navigator = global.window.navigator;
```

I am releasing a new test suite with Formsy today that uses this setup. You can check that out for more inspiration :-)

