Create an object to store the references in the parent component...

`this.myRefs = {};`

... and add this to your wrapped component in your parent component:

`<MyComponentWithinHoc onRef={item => { this.myRefs[myKey] = item; }} />`

item will contain the reference you need. Now add this to the HOC

```
componentDidMount() {
    if (this.props.onRef) {
        this.props.onRef(this.ref);
    }
}
```
